criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Aged 35-60 years male and female; Understand trial procedure and content and sign informed consent voluntarily;
2. No active skin disease on the face;
3. No facial filler such as hyaluronic acid or laser/light treatment;
4. No oral steroids,collagen powder/liquid,or topical hyaluronic acid used in the last 3 monthes;
5. No skin whitening products in the last 2 weeks.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. She is pregnant or in breast-feeding period;
2. To be allergic to trial medicine or its ingredient. No facial filler such as hyaluronic acid or laser/light treatment;
3. She/he had severe cardiovascular, cerebrovascular, renal, hepatic or hematopoietic disease;
4. She/he is taking part in the other clinical trial.
